[SN]TITLE[SN]
Mark Selby beats Ding Junhui to win World Snooker Championship

[SN]FIRST-SENTENCE[SN]
England's world number one Mark Selby beat China's Ding Junhui 18-14 to win his second World Championship title.

[SN]RESTBODY[SN]
